@SupportedSourceVersion(value=RELEASE_6)
@SupportedAnnotationTypes(value="com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.GenDispatch")
public class GenDispatchProcessor
extends GenProcessor

Processes GenDispatch annotations.

GenDispatchProcessor should only ever be called by tool infrastructure. See Processor for more details.
